:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Asian Stocks Fall on Tech, Brent Trades Above $100: Markets Wrap</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Momoka Yokoyama、Abhishek Vishnoi、Alice French.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a data-yga='{\"yInteractivityType\":\"0\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
